WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Put your phone into USPL mode

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Run the Rom Update Utility (RUU) for Blackstone 

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Carry out the steps as advised by the RUU program

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:07.000
RUU is now flashing custom ROM image into your phone.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:35.000
The update can take up to 8-10 minutes. Be patience...

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Fast-forwarding ...

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:22.000
Once finished, the phone will now reboot. 

00:02:24.000 --> 00:03:25.000
The first reboot, after an ROM update, can take up to a minute.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:04:16.000
Continue the Windows Mobile setup procedure as per normal.

